    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec variable M differential lock, providing a truly analog driving experience. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul to ensure the valvetrain remains precise. The chassis maintains excellent turn-in response thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted suspension setup. It is a well-maintained specimen that balances raw performance with high-speed stability, ready for the canyons or a spirited commute.",
      "price": 34500.0,
